@WalesOnline But the graph for this date (23rd Feb) shows around 450 inpatients being treated for covid

The PHW data for this date is shown below

You can see the error most clearly on 17th Jan. Over 850 on your graph, but only 581 on PHW data table https://t.co/Rr2PG1NXdp

